sentences: Julie Pinel (fl. 1710–1737) was a French composer and harpsichord teacher, born into the Pinel family of court musicians.
Nouveau recueil d'airs sérieux et à boirePinel published her collection of 31 songs, Nouveau receuil d'airs sérioux et à boire in 1737.
